  "desc": "For this nostalgic love song, I created the cover art, typography, and full visual design – all built to match the mood. Simple, slightly analog, emotional but not overdone. The goal was to make it feel familiar, like a memory, without being too sweet or polished.<br><br>The video was made together with Kooza, who, as always, nailed the vibe and turned it into something that just works – nothing overcomplicated, just emotion that hits right. The visuals support the track without spelling everything out.<br><br>While we were shooting the video, I also took a few photos that became part of the project – used for covers, promo, and visuals around the release. I also handled the overall visual direction, making sure everything stayed in the same mood.<br><br>A project made by feel – low-key, consistent, and honest.",
