  "desc": "A multidisciplinary project that merges design and music. Born from a live performance featuring original music and lyrics, Efemmera was formed and released their debut album NIE.ISTOTY. As the art director, I oversaw everything from naming the band and album to creating the branding, covers, video, retouching photography – and even did the makeup! The name Efemmera blends femme and era, reflecting the band’s identity and values. It represents something fleeting, coexisting with harsh reality, and striving for change through empathy.",
