  "big": "SBM FF24",
  "subtitle": "SBM Label",
  "desc": "To be honest, this is the biggest project I've had the chance to create so far. I was responsible for the entire visual identity of the festival – not just the key visual (KV), but also how it translated into the overall style of the event.<br><br>Together with Michulec (my design partner in crime at SBM), we created the logo, key visual, posters, merch, animations, stage design, teaser video, wristbands, web design… basically, a lot. And I have to say, it’s one of my favorite and most complex projects to date.<br><br>The whole concept is built around a sports theme, which connects directly to the festival's new location – the University of Physical Education. That’s where all the sports references come from.<br><br>It’s hard to describe everything we did in words, so here’s a visual recap of six months of work.",
