  "big": "Wine bottle label",
  "subtitle": "Winnica Katarzyna",
  "desc": "Together with our design team, we created a comprehensive visual identity for Winnica Katarzyna – including new wine labels, refreshed branding elements, and a cohesive corporate identity concept. Our goal was to capture and enhance the character of a brand that already had a strong story, energy, and voice, but lacked a unified visual presence.<br><br>We arrived at a place full of soul – a charming, family-run vineyard with the potential to speak authentically and powerfully to a new audience. We wanted to break down the distance between the brand and its potential customers – to lower the entry barrier and invite people into the world of wine in a natural, warm, and approachable way.<br><br>The new labels and visual identity became a carrier of what truly matters: the story of the place, the people, and their passion. We chose a visual language that blends an urban aesthetic with the charm of a rural, family vineyard – creating a wine that speaks for itself.",
